{"article":"<section><h1 id=\"easy-mock 接口使用\" data-index=0>easy-mock 接口使用</h1><section><h2 id=\"webpack 代理 devServer.proxy 无法使用 easy-mock 问题解决\" data-index=1>webpack 代理 devServer.proxy 无法使用 easy-mock 问题解决</h2><p>手动增加可访问的 cookie、host 请求头信息</p><pre><code class=lang-js>devServer: {\n  <span class=hljs-attr>contentBase</span>: path.resolve(__dirname, <span class=hljs-string>'dist'</span>),\n  <span class=hljs-attr>host</span>: <span class=hljs-string>'192.168.1.222'</span>,\n  <span class=hljs-attr>port</span>: <span class=hljs-number>3001</span>,\n  <span class=hljs-attr>inline</span>: <span class=hljs-literal>true</span>,\n  <span class=hljs-attr>hot</span>: <span class=hljs-literal>true</span>,\n  <span class=hljs-attr>hotOnly</span>: <span class=hljs-literal>false</span>,\n  <span class=hljs-attr>proxy</span>: {\n    <span class=hljs-string>\"/Publisher\"</span>: {\n      <span class=hljs-attr>target</span>: <span class=hljs-string>\"http://www.easy-mock.com/mock/59c46dbfe0dc663341b4084a/example\"</span>,\n\n      <span class=hljs-attr>onProxyRes</span>: <span class=hljs-function><span class=hljs-keyword>function</span>(<span class=hljs-params>proxyRes, req, res</span>)</span>{\n      },\n      <span class=hljs-attr>onProxyReq</span>: <span class=hljs-function><span class=hljs-keyword>function</span>(<span class=hljs-params>proxyReq, req, res</span>)</span>{\n        proxyReq.setHeader(<span class=hljs-string>'Cookie'</span>,<span class=hljs-string>'Cookie:easy-mock_token=eyJ0eXAiOiJKV1QiLCJhbGciOiJIUzI1NiJ9.eyJqdGkiOiI1OWM0NmRiZmUwZGM2NjMzNDFiNDA4NTIiLCJleHAiOjE1MDcyNTQ5NzUsImlkIjoiNTljNDZkYmZlMGRjNjYzMzQxYjQwODQ5IiwiaWF0IjoxNTA2MDQ1Mzc1fQ.45-Ow-W-lcq1oxIn-japLDd95lSAZMnnBuaCDhTZULA'</span>)\n        proxyReq.setHeader(<span class=hljs-string>'Host'</span>,<span class=hljs-string>'www.easy-mock.com'</span>)\n      }\n    }\n  }\n}\n</code></pre></section></section><section><h1 id=\"glob 路径匹配\" data-index=2>glob 路径匹配</h1><section><h2 id=\"glob 介绍\" data-index=3>glob 介绍</h2><p><a href=https://github.com/isaacs/node-glob>英文</a></p><p><a href=http://www.jianshu.com/p/ce7cf53274bb>中文</a></p></section><section><h2 id=监听所有目录，所有文件 data-index=4>监听所有目录，所有文件</h2><p>&#39;./src/**&#39;</p></section></section><section><h1 id=代码规范 data-index=5>代码规范</h1><p><a href=https://eslint.org/ >https://eslint.org/</a></p><p><a href=https://github.com/standard/standard/blob/master/docs/README-zhcn.md>JavaScript Standard Style</a></p></section><section><h1 id=前端框架工具汇总 data-index=6>前端框架工具汇总</h1><section><h2 id=前端构建 data-index=7>前端构建</h2><p>gulp 与 browserify<br>webpack<br>rollup</p></section><section><h2 id=各种js数据驱动框架 data-index=8>各种js数据驱动框架</h2><ul><li>reactjs</li><li>vuejs</li><li><a href=https://github.com/developit/preact>Preact</a>：react 的轻量解决方案</li></ul></section></section><section><h1 id=浏览器跨域 data-index=9>浏览器跨域</h1><section><h2 id=\"h5 解决方案\" data-index=10>h5 解决方案</h2><p>允许单个:</p><pre><code>Access-Control-Allow-Origin: https:<span class=hljs-comment>//www.google.com</span>\n</code></pre><p>允许多个，逗号隔开:</p><pre><code>Access-Control-Allow-Origin: https:<span class=hljs-comment>//www.google.com,https://www.baidu.com</span>\n</code></pre><p>允许所有:</p><pre><code>Access-Control-Allow-Origin: *\n</code></pre></section></section><section><h1 id=移动端web data-index=11>移动端web</h1><section><h2 id=\"ios 移动端 click 300ms 延迟解决\" data-index=12>ios 移动端 click 300ms 延迟解决</h2><p>文本框点击获焦也会出现延迟</p><p><strong>解决：</strong></p><p>head 中添加如下代码即可</p><pre><code class=lang-html><span class=hljs-tag>&lt;<span class=hljs-name>meta</span> <span class=hljs-attr>name</span>=<span class=hljs-string>\"viewport\"</span> <span class=hljs-attr>content</span>=<span class=hljs-string>\"width=device-width,initial-scale=1,user-scalable=no\"</span>/&gt;</span>\n</code></pre><p>强调，必须带有<code>width=device-width</code><br>此方式也会禁止双击放大</p><p>当前测试系统为ios10，由于条件问题，其他低版本系统未测</p></section><section><h2 id=\"android webview 初始body 为0 问题\" data-index=13>android webview 初始body 为0 问题</h2></section><section><h2 id=\"android webview 界面残留，界面闪烁\" data-index=14>android webview 界面残留，界面闪烁</h2><p>关闭硬件加速</p></section><section><h2 id=打电话 data-index=15>打电话</h2><pre><code class=lang-html><span class=hljs-tag>&lt;<span class=hljs-name>a</span> <span class=hljs-attr>href</span>=<span class=hljs-string>\"tel:13670026449\"</span>&gt;</span>客服热线<span class=hljs-tag>&lt;/<span class=hljs-name>a</span>&gt;</span>\n</code></pre><p>android 支持。ios 微信网页也支持，其他未测</p><p><a href=http://www.cnblogs.com/softwarelanguagebs/p/5490837.html>Android网页中tel等协议参考</a></p><p><a href=http://lucaslz.com/2016/08/24/tips/callphone-sendmessage-composeemail/ >ios 参考</a></p></section></section>","menu":"<div class=\"menu-item fold\"><div class=\"item\" data-index=\"0\"><i class=\"\"></i><span class=\"txt\">easy-mock 接口使用</span></div><div class=\"list\"><div class=\"menu-item fold\"><div class=\"item\" data-index=\"1\"><i class=\"hidden\"></i><span class=\"txt\">webpack 代理 devServer.proxy 无法使用 easy-mock 问题解决</span></div><div class=\"list\"></div></div></div></div><div class=\"menu-item fold\"><div class=\"item\" data-index=\"2\"><i class=\"\"></i><span class=\"txt\">glob 路径匹配</span></div><div class=\"list\"><div class=\"menu-item fold\"><div class=\"item\" data-index=\"3\"><i class=\"hidden\"></i><span class=\"txt\">glob 介绍</span></div><div class=\"list\"></div></div><div class=\"menu-item fold\"><div class=\"item\" data-index=\"4\"><i class=\"hidden\"></i><span class=\"txt\">监听所有目录，所有文件</span></div><div class=\"list\"></div></div></div></div><div class=\"menu-item fold\"><div class=\"item\" data-index=\"5\"><i class=\"hidden\"></i><span class=\"txt\">代码规范</span></div><div class=\"list\"></div></div><div class=\"menu-item fold\"><div class=\"item\" data-index=\"6\"><i class=\"\"></i><span class=\"txt\">前端框架工具汇总</span></div><div class=\"list\"><div class=\"menu-item fold\"><div class=\"item\" data-index=\"7\"><i class=\"hidden\"></i><span class=\"txt\">前端构建</span></div><div class=\"list\"></div></div><div class=\"menu-item fold\"><div class=\"item\" data-index=\"8\"><i class=\"hidden\"></i><span class=\"txt\">各种js数据驱动框架</span></div><div class=\"list\"></div></div></div></div><div class=\"menu-item fold\"><div class=\"item\" data-index=\"9\"><i class=\"\"></i><span class=\"txt\">浏览器跨域</span></div><div class=\"list\"><div class=\"menu-item fold\"><div class=\"item\" data-index=\"10\"><i class=\"hidden\"></i><span class=\"txt\">h5 解决方案</span></div><div class=\"list\"></div></div></div></div><div class=\"menu-item fold\"><div class=\"item\" data-index=\"11\"><i class=\"\"></i><span class=\"txt\">移动端web</span></div><div class=\"list\"><div class=\"menu-item fold\"><div class=\"item\" data-index=\"12\"><i class=\"hidden\"></i><span class=\"txt\">ios 移动端 click 300ms 延迟解决</span></div><div class=\"list\"></div></div><div class=\"menu-item fold\"><div class=\"item\" data-index=\"13\"><i class=\"hidden\"></i><span class=\"txt\">android webview 初始body 为0 问题</span></div><div class=\"list\"></div></div><div class=\"menu-item fold\"><div class=\"item\" data-index=\"14\"><i class=\"hidden\"></i><span class=\"txt\">android webview 界面残留，界面闪烁</span></div><div class=\"list\"></div></div><div class=\"menu-item fold\"><div class=\"item\" data-index=\"15\"><i class=\"hidden\"></i><span class=\"txt\">打电话</span></div><div class=\"list\"></div></div></div></div>"}